CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 24, 2013

[Cite as 12/24/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-Ohio-5678.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2013-1166. State ex rel. Daily Servs., Inc. v. Buehrer.

In Mandamus and Prohibition. On motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, Kennedy, French, and O’Neill, JJ., concur.
